Terms and conditions
.sp 3mm
1. Using your card
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
You can be issued a MasterCard Debit card linked to an account at
&BANKNAVN. on the basis of an individual assessment as agreed.
The card is a debit card with balance check, and you can use it
in Denmark and abroad. You may not use the card
for unlawful purposes, including the purchase of goods or services that
are illegal according to local legislation.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
1.1. Use of the card as a payment card in Denmark and abroad
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You can use the card to pay for goods and services from payment recipients
who accept MasterCard as a means of payment, including payment recipients
on the Internet.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In addition, you can use the card to make mail or telephone order
purchases and to make payments in self-service machines. If you have an
account owing in your favour from a payment recipient, the payment
recipient can use your card to deposit the money on your account.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
MasterCard on mobile phone can be used when making physical purchases from
payment recipients accepting contactless cards.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Individual payment recipients may apply regulations that limit use of your
card.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. and PBS accept no liability for a payment recipient refusing to
accept the card as a means of payment.
.sp 3mm
We accept no liability for any faults or defects in the services supplied
by the payment recipient.
