Mail order purchases
:SKRSLUT.
.br
When making mail order purchases, you need to sign the order form to
confirm that the company is allowed to deduct the sum from your card
account. When you state your card number orally or in writing with the
purpose of having the transaction charged to your card, this is
considered approval of the transaction.
